      "text": "Chile 🇨🇱 is beginning to revel in having ousted Gabriel Boric from power. In a stunning operation, Trinidad Steinert, Chile's Minister of Security, reported that within 72 hours, three thousand fugitives were captured. \n\n“This operation, carried out by Chilean investigative teams and the Carabineros (police), lasted three days: March 12, 13, and 14. It was a resounding success, a major blow because the total number of people with arrest warrants was three thousand. In addition, cars, drugs, and weapons were seized. We're not going to stop; we're going to continue after them all.”\n\nGovernments choose to be complicit in crime, this is why Boric never cared to catch these people.",
